                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-233-off1287 t18261026-233-crimeloc1291"></join>. On the morning of the 22d of October, the prisoners came into my shop, between six and seven o'clock, with another person - they asked for a roll and butter - I went to the kitchen for the butler - they paid me - Owen gave me information - I looked, and missed two weights, and have not found them.</p>
